                                 5.1 
                              ), Drug Interactions (

                                 7.3 
                              ), and Clinical Pharmacology (


                                    12.3

                              )].

The dose of simvastatin tablets USP should not exceed 20 mg/day [see Warnings and Precautions (

                                 5.1 
                              ), Drug Interactions (

